<P>
A Stockton man was killed and his 13-year-old companion wounded early Friday in 
a drive-by shooting police said may be gang related. Jesse Horn Jr., 19, was 
shot fatally as he and the 13-year-old walked down the street near Gleason Park 
in downtown Stockton about midnight, authorities said. The 13-year-old was 
hospitalized in stable condition. 
</P>
